contentrichtext.text: '''Zzyzx''', '''Zyzzyx''', '''Zzyzx Road''' or '''Zyzzx Road''', usually pronounced {{IPAc-en|ˈ|z|aɪ|z|ɨ|k|s}}, may refer to: * [[Zzyzx, California]], U.S., and Zzyzx Road, a road leading to it * "Zzyzx Rd.", a song by Stone Sour from ''[[Come What(ever) May]]'' * "Zzyzx Scarecrow", a song by the band [[Stavesacre]] * [[Zzyzx (album)|''Zzyzx'' (album)]], an album by Zeromancer * [[Zzyzx (film)|''Zzyzx'' (film)]], a 2005 film directed by Richard Halpern * Zzyzx, a fictional company in the TV series ''[[Kyle XY]]'' * Zzyzx, a fictional prison for demons in the novel series ''[[Fablehaven]]'' by Brandon Mull ==See also== * [[Xyzzy]], a magic word from the computer game ''Colossal Cave Adventure'' * ''[[Zyzyxia lundellii]]'', a species of tropical shrub * Zyzz, is the persona that was used by Australian bodybuilder [[Aziz Shavershian]] * [[Zyzzyx]], a genus of sand wasp * ''[[Zyzzyx Road]]'', a 2006 film directed by John Penney * ''[[Zzyzzyxx]]'', a 1982 arcade game {{disambig}}
